2 Data description
Do you plan to transcribe interviews to textual files? If so, then also include those in the list. 
3. Legal and ethical
Since you are doing interviews with people, and therefore processing personal data, you will have to submit a PRET application and include the approval number in your DMP: https://admin.kuleuven.be/privacy/en/studpers/index
4. Documentation
What about documentation of archival materials? Will you create a catalogue / database with annotation / coding for those materials? 
5. Data security
Consider whether recordings of interviews (from which interviewees are probably identifiable) will be destroyed after transcription or not. Indicate that here. 

Please submit an updated version of the DMP as intermediate  DMP in a few months time, once you have all this information ready.
